			  			I am new to the game so I fully expect to get &quot;flamed&quot; but it seems to me that the only thing I don't like about AS is the abilty to rape someone.  The way the game is set up I believe that you should not be able to engage someone without going to war with them.  And furthermore should not be able to go to war instantly.  Maybe make the person declaring war wait for an hour or so before being able to attack.  As it is now it boils down to if you are online at the specific time you get war declared on you then you can have a &quot;fair&quot; war. If you are not online say went to the store or in the bathroom for 20 minutes you could come back and find that for example someone high powered had come in and blockaded you and destroyed your fleet then there low powered friend can come in and take your undefended planets.  I realize that part of that can be avoided by stationing fleets on planets but if you have hundreds of planets it is hardly feasable to set every planets defense plan and maintain everything it would be a 24 hour 7 day job just to maintain a sturdy defense.<br />
<br />
Am I the only one who feels this way?						<P align=right> </P>
